		<description><![CDATA[Graham and Green has become the elegant choice when purchasing beautiful high quality furniture, which oozes style and sophistication. Inspired by experiences and traditional furniture found in the most far-flung and exotic parts of the world, at Graham and Green we offer collections based on cultural and traditional flair. You will find pieces of furniture, [...]]]></description>
			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><strong>Graham and Green has become the elegant choice when purchasing beautiful high quality furniture, which oozes style and sophistication.</strong> Inspired by experiences and traditional furniture found in the most far-flung and exotic parts of the world, at Graham and Green we offer collections based on cultural and traditional flair. You will find pieces of furniture, which echo the spices and scents of Morocco, the chic, suave, classic lines of Paris. The antique, distressed styles of a French country farmhouse and the delicate floral patterns of Asia.</p><p>Graham and Green not only create beautiful furniture, which hosts elements of different countries of the world, but also different eras. Art deco, the 30’s and 40’s prove a great inspiration to us when we design our furniture.</p><p>We love shabby chic, we love contemporary, we love clean lines and comfort. Our collections are inspired by travel, by experiences and by history, it’s a mix of old and new, and we think a lot about our surroundings at home. We also look at modern design in the home, and incorporate it into our furniture. We hope that conveys in the furniture and home accessories we offer to our customers.</p><p>Graham and Green began back in 1974. We have grown considerably, have two shops in London, 4 catalogues a year and a website, which customers can purchase from.</p><p>You will find everything you need to decorate your house and create a beautiful, serene, atmospheric home, from tables and chairs, sofas, mirrors, lighting, soft furnishings and furniture for the garden.</p><p>We have a great loyal base of customers who are overwhelmed by the quality and beauty of our furniture and we are pleased to attract new customers all the time. You can really see why, we love the furniture we source, design and produce and we want to share these pieces with you, our customers, to make your home a desirable place to live, relax and grow.</p><p>Visit the online store at www.grahamandgreen.co.uk to view and purchase pieces, plus you can request their seasonal catalogue.</p>]]></content:encoded>
