		<description><![CDATA[Need to get your clothing in order? Can’t find those pair of trousers or shirt you need for work. Get your clothing in line with Hanger King Pro!Hanger King Pro helps you arrange your wardrobe to be neat, tidy and save you lots of room by tripling the space in your wardrobe.This amazing coat hanger [...]]]></description>
			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Need to get your clothing in order? Can’t find those pair of trousers or shirt you need for work. Get your clothing in line with Hanger King Pro!</p><p>Hanger King Pro helps you arrange your wardrobe to be neat, tidy and save you lots of room by tripling the space in your wardrobe.</p><p>This amazing coat hanger is specially shaped for every type of garment of any size and it makes sure they stay put.</p><p>Hanger King Pro will take:</p><p>- Skirts<br />- Jackets<br />- Trousers<br />- Shorts<br />- Shirts<br />- Tops<br />- Knitted items<br />- Evening wear<br />- Belts<br />- Ties<br />- Scarves</p><p>And many more items, saving you lots of space to hang everything in your wardrobe.</p><p>There is no more worry about clothing slipping off and ending at the bottom of the wardrobe, the special anti-static grips make sure even satin and silk stay in place, and the special bars and clips keep trousers and skirts on the hanger.</p><p>Jumper necks being stretched out of shape? Not any more with Hanger King Pro, the specially shaped neck makes sure that every item stays in place and in shape, plus the hanger shoulders protect and prevent snagging on the most delicate fabrics.</p><p>Another great feature of the Hanger King Pro is the ability to hang numerous items on one hanger with its amazing drop loop system, which allows you to attach another hanger below and so on. This means you can have everything together is sections and you can see exactly what you have to wear in your wardrobe. This also reduces the space you take up putting items on hangers, which get bunched up on the rail and end up on the floor.</p><p>Hanger King Pro is a fantastic household item to keep clothing in check, and not only is it incredibly practical it looks fantastic too. Hanger King Pro is an item everyone should own in his or her wardrobes.</p>]]></content:encoded>
